OL,3,CElection rule changes see more than
OL,4,C2,400 new voters
OL,6,FMore than 2,400 new islanders were
OL,7,Frecorded voting in this year's
OL,8,FJersey's election when compared to
OL,9,F2022, official figures show.
OL,11,FStatistics from vote.je found it was
OL,12,Fan improvement of almost 9% since the
OL,13,Felection four years ago.
OL,15,FThis year, several key changes were
OL,16,Fmade to increase voter numbers,
OL,17,Fincluding Automatic Voter Registration
OL,18,F(AVR), which meant any islander who
OL,19,Fwas eligible to vote was automatically
OL,20,Fput on the electoral roll.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
