OL,3,CElection rule changes see more than
OL,4,C2,400 new voters
OL,6,FIt meant that more than 24,000 people
OL,7,Fwere registered this year.
OL,9,FOther measures to boost turnout
OL,10,Fincluded moving polling day to a
OL,11,FSunday and relaxing eligibility
OL,12,Fcriteria.
OL,14,FIt was also hoped that introducing
OL,15,FSenators - who are elected on an
OL,16,Fisland-wide mandate - would encourage
OL,17,Fmore people to head to the polls.
OL,19,FSenatorial Results by Parish
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
