OL,3,CElection rule changes see more than
OL,4,C2,400 new voters
OL,6,FSt Mary was the only parish to see
OL,7,Fmore than 50% of registered voters
OL,8,Fcast a ballot, with a turnout of 53.1%.
OL,10,FThe lowest figure was in St Helier,
OL,11,Fwhere just 22.2% of people went to the
OL,12,Fpolls.
OL,14,FRecord female representation
OL,16,FThe 2026 election also returned a
OL,17,Frecord number of women winning seats
OL,18,Fin the States Assembly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
