OL,3,CElection rule changes see more than
OL,4,C2,400 new voters
OL,6,FIt is now the highest number of women
OL,7,Fpoliticians the States Chamber has
OL,8,Fhad, sitting at 45%. The increase was
OL,9,Fjust one more than the previous States
OL,10,FAssembly, and shows a continued upward
OL,11,Ftrend since 2010.
OL,13,FA vote for the status quo?
OL,15,FWhilst the election saw some dramatic
OL,16,Fresults, the number of returning
OL,17,Fcandidates makes up two thirds of the
OL,18,FChamber.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
