OL,3,CElection rule changes see more than
OL,4,C2,400 new voters
OL,6,FIn terms of political parties, Reform
OL,7,FJersey saw some of its key members
OL,8,Flose seats, reducing their presence in
OL,9,Fthe States Chamber from ten to seven.
OL,11,FValue Jersey is not a political party,
OL,12,Fbut now has six sitting politicians in
OL,13,Fthe Assembly who are endorsing their
OL,14,Fpolicies.
OL,16,FPeople First fielded two candidates
OL,17,Ffor St Helier South's Deputy race, but
OL,18,Ffailed to secure a seat.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
