OL,3,CElection rule changes see more than
OL,4,C2,400 new voters
OL,6,FOverall, independent candidates still
OL,7,Fdominated the results, with 36 of the
OL,8,F49 members not associated with any
OL,9,Fparty.
OL,11,FAs Jersey returns from the polls, ITV
OL,12,FChannel breaks down the key election
OL,13,Fresults. Listen to Jersey Votes
OL,14,Fwherever you get your podcasts or
OL,15,Fwatch on ITVX, and YouTube below.
